## Loading Packages

```{r}
library(curl)
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)
```

```{r}
f_AllBirth <- curl("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sadams32/BI510-Final/refs/heads/main/AllBirthData.csv") 

d_AllBirth <- read.csv(f_AllBirth, header = TRUE, sep = ",", stringsAsFactors = TRUE) # read in data

head(d_AllBirth) # preview
```
